OL,3,C'A friend to all' - tribute to
OL,4,Cteenager who died after a collision
OL,6,FThe family of a teenager who died
OL,7,Ffollowing a collision in Haslingden
OL,8,Fhave paid an emotional tribute,
OL,9,Fdescribing her as a 'friend to all'.
OL,11,FVictoria Niebylska, 18, was a
OL,12,Fpassenger in a VW Golf which collided
OL,13,Fwith the side of a house and retaining
OL,14,Fwall on Helmshore Road on Monday night.
OL,16,FVery sadly, Victoria passed away in
OL,17,Fhospital the following day.
OL,19,FPaying tribute, the family said: "My
OL,20,Fonly daughter, beloved granddaughter
OL,21,Fand friend to all.
OL,26,@{D@bOU
