OL,3,C'A friend to all' - tribute to
OL,4,Cteenager who died after a collision
OL,6,F"Eighteen years could never hold all
OL,7,Fthe love you brought into this world.
OL,8,FYou were my one and only, my greatest
OL,9,Fjoy, my whole heart.
OL,11,F"So deeply cherished, so dearly
OL,12,Fmissed, yet forever with us in every
OL,13,Fheartbeat, every memory, every quiet
OL,14,Fmoment.
OL,16,F"Your love remains, always Mum, Nan
OL,17,Fand Grandad.
OL,19,F"Forever 18."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU{D@MO]
