OL,3,C'A friend to all' - tribute to
OL,4,Cteenager who died after a collision
OL,6,FThe emergency services were called at
OL,7,F11.49pm on Monday (4th May) to
OL,8,FHelmshore Road at the junction with
OL,9,FDean Road, to a report of a collision.
OL,11,FThe driver of the VW Golf, a man in
OL,12,Fhis 20s, was pronounced deceased in
OL,13,Fhospital on Tuesday morning.
OL,15,FAnother passenger in the car, an 18-
OL,16,Fyear-old girl, suffered serious
OL,17,Finjuries and remains in hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
