OL,3,C'A friend to all' - tribute to
OL,4,Cteenager who died after a collision
OL,6,FLancashire Police officers
OL,7,Finvestigating the collision are
OL,8,Fcontinuing to appeal for witnesses and
OL,9,Fany dashcam/CCTV/Ring Doorbell footage
OL,10,Ffrom the area.
OL,12,FPlease contact us on 101, quoting log
OL,13,F1623 of 4th May, or email our Serious
OL,14,FCollision Investigation Unit at
OL,15,FSCIU@lancashire.police.uk
